commit message: Fixed TopExceptionHandler, removed bugreports for some SQLiteExceptions
Slight improvement on startup performance, still much to do...

- Initialize TopExceptionHandler already in MyApplication
- Merge local implementation of AsyncTask from Android-Source

- Async DB-Access
- Async initialization of HTTP-Cache
- Asnyc purging of orphaned articles, also only once per session

- Set theme in all activities to resolve errors on api level 8
- Move update of title and unread data into background, only start once, call UI when finished
- Change layout of locale plugin
Filter old api levels in TopExceptionHandler

- Removed unnecessary function calls
- Added debug output to long running operations
- Changelog
Reduced article limit to speed up db operations, 5k should be enough
Fixed bug that slowed down article fetching
Only cleanup database once a day

== Version 1.71 ==
* Moved lots of stuff to the background so the UI should be more responsive
* Fixed several bugs introduced with the christmas-update
* Fixed a bug that slowed down article fetching quite much
